      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Fraud Detection using the Model",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Fraud Detection using the Model",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "9gN9fPAZBjX0x5aJ8e31o",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2384.5851980854286,
      "y": 59672.06034612523,
      "width": 638,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bZ6",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 936647102,
      "version": 265,
      "versionNonce": 562909943,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777046636069,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Fraud detection service is simpler HTTP service that\n- Loads the model from S3.\n- Creates in memory structure to classify the transactions\n- exposes API to do the synchronously.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Fraud detection service is simpler HTTP service that\n- Loads the model from S3.\n- Creates in memory structure to classify the transactions\n- exposes API to do the synchronously.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "3QbdPec_iFxDKtoOKPauy",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2378.844030726848,
      "y": 59796.419607066,
      "width": 1210,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bZ7",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 565685374,
      "version": 250,
      "versionNonce": 115260409,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777046636069,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The end user facing transaction API invokes Fraud Detection to understand if it is fraudelent or not - FIG 1.6\nIf not then transaction proceeds,\nIf yes, customer service is invloved & notificaion is sent to user.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The end user facing transaction API invokes Fraud Detection to understand if it is fraudelent or not - FIG 1.6\nIf not then transaction proceeds,\nIf yes, customer service is invloved & notificaion is sent to user.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
