      "updated": 1777005103599,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "You have never made a purchage > 10,000 Rs but amazon recommending\n1,50,000 Rs laptop.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "You have never made a purchage > 10,000 Rs but amazon recommending\n1,50,000 Rs laptop.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "X2NUknXmRx-8asRj8SG8R",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2402.779865820018,
      "y": 62054.906638223125,
      "width": 858,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#fd7e14",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bZR",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 795983031,
      "version": 151,
      "versionNonce": 152951929,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777005124839,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- This approach completely lacks personalization\n- It wastes space by recommending items a user has already bought, or items\n  that are completely irrelevant (e.g., recommending a 150,000 rupee laptop to\n  someone who only buys items under 10,000 rupees)\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- This approach completely lacks personalization\n- It wastes space by recommending items a user has already bought, or items\n  that are completely irrelevant (e.g., recommending a 150,000 rupee laptop to\n  someone who only buys items under 10,000 rupees)\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "GC-mRIkxjE9HzGecDVjxM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2382.8315700676117,
      "y": 62260.32015254746,
      "width": 1298,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#fd7e14",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bZS",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1777926167,
      "version": 88,
      "versionNonce": 201256729,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777005162669,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "A well-designed recommendation feed blends two main approaches to balance what a user already likes with fresh content",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A well-designed recommendation feed blends two main approaches to balance what a user already likes with fresh content",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Kyfeshny47DxrLo7mMlRx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2387.73627335108,
      "y": 62200.163093938725,
      "width": 523.5997924804688,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "#fd7e14",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bZT",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 829521881,
      "version": 58,
      "versionNonce": 646728855,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777005160989,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Core Machine Learning Approaches: ",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Core Machine Learning Approaches: ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yb7XstS0_ian0D55cfDdd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2385.7473021625397,
      "y": 62358.56499079768,
      "width": 647.7072143554688,
      "height": 32.72281633267994,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "#fd7e14",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bZU",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1149319031,
      "version": 106,
      "versionNonce": 1408585977,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777046083844,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Approach #1. Content Filtering (Exploitation)",
      "fontSize": 26.178253066143952,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Approach #1. Content Filtering (Exploitation)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "2F1Czy-qO7iq5btKiyAQ7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2393.4250618533342,
      "y": 62440.72233592284,
      "width": 1056,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#fd7e14",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bZV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 535093975,
      "version": 86,
      "versionNonce": 1330625849,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777005218649,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Concept: Recommends items that are similar to what the user has already consumed, searched for, \nor bought. It \"exploits\" the user's known preferences to keep them engaged in a specific niche \n(e.g., showing more physics books after buying a physics book)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Concept: Recommends items that are similar to what the user has already consumed, searched for, \nor bought. It \"exploits\" the user's known preferences to keep them engaged in a specific niche \n(e.g., showing more physics books after buying a physics book)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Lv64BniG2FxE4Snxdg2Dl",
